title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 109: Featuring John-Michael Liles + Barstool Big Cat
description:
On a Thursday episode of Spittin' Chiclets, the guys are joined by Barstool Big Cat, and former NHL defenseman John-Michael Liles. With the guys previewing the Central division, Big Cat joins to break down the Chicago Blackhawks and what to expect out of them next season. The guys then talk to John-Michael Liles who was one of the most underrated interviews since Spittin' Chiclets started. JML talks about his time in Colorado, Boston and a ton more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
